│ PHIs (threadBinOpOverSelect/threadBinOpOverPHI). For operations that may trap │
│ or are undefined (such as division by zero), that threading can be unsafe if  │
│ a divisor may be zero on any path. InstCombine itself guards against such     │
│ speculation in foldVectorBinop using                                          │
