│ preserving the original semantics.                                            │
│                                                                               │
│ 4. Proposed Edit Point(s)                                                     │
│ We add a safety guard in InstructionSimplify::simplifyDivRem before threading │
│ the binop over a select for div/rem. Only allow threading if we can prove the │
│ divisor is known non-zero on all paths. This prevents speculative execution   │
│ over potentially undefined div-by-zero.                                       │
│                                                                               │
